title: Emmy Rossum's Flower Girls Upstaged Her at Her Wedding

json.text: EMMY, CONGRATULATIONS ARE IN ORDER, YOU RECENTLY GOT MARRIED.
>> I DID.
>> James: HOW WAS THE WEDDING, WAS ITS EXACTLY AS YOU
PICTURED IT AND IMAGINED IT?
>> IT KIND OF WAS.
I WAS HAVING LOTS OF NIGHTMARES LEADING UP TO IT, AS A BAD
BRIDES DO.
YOUR DRESS DOESN'T FIT OR YOU WALK DOWN THE AISLE NAKED, NONE
OF THAT HAPPENED, THANK GOD BUT THERE WAS ONE SMALL THING
THRAPPED RIGHT BEFORE I WENT DOWN THE AISLE.
I DON'T HAVE A HUGE FAMILY, IT WASN'T A LARGE WEDDING.
I HAD TWO FLOWER GIRLS THAT WERE BOTH ABOUT THREE YEARS OLD.
IT WAS GOING TO BE AH ADORABLE AND I THINK IT WAS ADORABLE.
I DIDN'T SEE WHAT ACTUALLY REALLY HAPPENED BECAUSE THEY
WENT OUT FIRST AND I WAS LIKE PEEKING BEHIND THE DOORS.
IT WAS DURING THEIR NAP TIME.
SO ONE OF THE GIRLS WAS QUITE CRANKY AND NOT FEELING IT AT
ALL.
>> YOU COULD HAVE GOTTEN AROUND THAT.
>> I COULD HAVE SCHEDULED IT EARLIER.
THE OTHER GIRL WAS QUITE A DIVA ABOUT IT.
WHEN THE CRANKY GIRL NOTICED THE DIVA WAS GETTING QUITE A BIT OF
ATTENTION, SHE RAN UP THE AISLE THROWING HER PETALS AT THE OARL
GIRL, LIKE A WOMEN'S WRESTLING FIGHT BROKE OUT.
THEY WERE LIKE THROWING THEIR BASKETS, THEY THREW THEM AT EACH
OTHER.
THEY UPSTAGED ME AT MY OWN WEDDING.
>> James: FANTASTIC, WERE YOU LIKE, SAYING GO BACK IN THIS IS
A DIFFERENT THING.
>> WHEN I GOT UP THERE THE RABBI WAS LIKE WOW YOU'RE GLAD YOU'RE
FAMOUS BECAUSE THESE GIRLS STOLE YOUR SPOTLIGHT.
JOKE, JUST GOES TO SHOW THERE'S SOMEONE YOUNGER AND CUTER COMING
DOWN THE AISLE!
